name: stillborn
description:
have you arrived. are you in arrival. are you unarrived yet. have you been arriving for two years. for ten days. are in arriving. are you arrived, do you arrive habitually, or are you unarrived yet. are you unarrived yet.

{ }

Please use headphones! For the best experience

Made for the Twine Poetry Jam in less than 48 hours.
